$ (unknown no. of lines missing)
1. [... ...] X X [...]
#lem: X; X; X; X; X
#etcsl: line-id=1

2. [... ...] X ba-ni-ŋar-re#-[eš]
#lem: X; X; X; ŋar[put]
#etcsl: line-id=2

3. nam-lugal-ŋa₂ ud-bi sud-da#
#lem: namlugal[kingship]; ud[sun]; sud[distant]
#etcsl: line-id=3

4. bal-ŋa₂ he₂-ŋal₂ pa ed₂-ed₂-dam
#lem: bala[turn]; heŋal[plenty]; pa[branch]; e[leave]
#etcsl: line-id=4

5. {d}en-ki en dug₄-ga-ni nu-kur₂-ru saŋ il₂ ba-ni-kur₉
#lem: Enkik[1]DN; en[lord]; dug[speak]; kur[different]; saŋ[head]; il[raise]; kur[enter]
#etcsl: line-id=5

6. {d}utu inim-ma-ni saŋ-ba du maškim-še₃ ma-an-šum₂
#lem: Utu[1]DN; inim[word]; saŋ[head]; ŋen[go]; maškim[an administrator]; šum[give]
#etcsl: line-id=6

7. {d}nin-lil₂ kalam-ma gu₃ hul₂-la ma-ni-de₂-a-ke₄-eš₂
#lem: Ninlil[1]DN; kalam[the Land (of Sumer)]; gu[voice]; hul[rejoice]; de[pour]
#etcsl: line-id=7

8. unken-na ŋizzal ma-ni-ak-ke₄-eš₂
#lem: unkin[assembly]; ŋizzal[hearing]; ak[do]
#etcsl: line-id=8

9. šul-gi sipad zid ki-en-gi-ra-me#-[en]
#lem: Šulgir[1]RN; sipad[shepherd]; zid[right]; Kengir[1]
#etcsl: line-id=9

10. ŋa₂-ŋiš-šu₂-a e₂ di si im#-sa₂#-[...] X-[na]
#lem: Ŋaŋiššua[1]TN; e[house]; did[lawsuit]; si[horn]; sa[equal]; X
#etcsl: line-id=10

11. e₂ mah nam-[nin]-a tum₂-ma-na
#lem: e[house]; mah[great]; namnin[ladyship]; tum[suitable]
#etcsl: line-id=11

12. {e₂}pa-pah ki u₆# di kur-kur-ra ni₂# huš# gur₃-ru-na
#lem: papah[cella]; ki[place]; u[admiration]; di[speak]; kur[mountain(s)]; ni[fear]; huš[reddish]; gur[lift]
#etcsl: line-id=12

13. e₂ X X [...] GI# šag₄-bi-a silim mu-na#-X-[dug₄]
#lem: e[house]; X; X; X; X; šag[heart]; silim[healthy]; dug[speak]
#etcsl: line-id=13

14. [... ...] mu-da-ab#-du₃ DA NI X [...] mu-|DU.DU| X [...]
#lem: X; X; du[build]; X; X; X; X; X; X; X
#etcsl: line-id=14

15. X gu₂ mu-da-ab#-[...]
#lem: X; gu[neck]; X
#etcsl: line-id=15

16. urud niŋ₂ kalag-ga-a X [...]
#lem: urud[copper]; niŋ[thing]; kalag[strong]; X; X
#etcsl: line-id=16

17. lu₂ hul-ŋal₂ {ŋiš}tukul-la mu-ši-[... X-a]
#lem: lu[person]; huluŋal[evil]; tukul[weapon]; X; X
#etcsl: line-id=17

18. a₂ aŋ₂-ŋa₂-ni-ta me₃-a mu-ni-gaz-a
#lem: a[arm]; aŋ[measure]; me[battle]; gaz[kill]
#etcsl: line-id=18

19. ur-saŋ gal-gal mu-til-la-ŋu₁₀ bar-ba im-mi-X
#lem: ursaŋ[warrior]; gal[big]; til[complete]; bar[outside]; X
#etcsl: line-id=19

20. gu₂-bi-a ŋiri₃-ŋu₁₀ im-mi-gub
#lem: gu[neck]; ŋiri[foot]; gub[stand]
#etcsl: line-id=20

21. ki-gal-ba ni₂-ŋu₁₀ saŋ im-ma-ni-il₂
#lem: kigal[platform]; ni[self]; saŋ[head]; il[raise]
#etcsl: line-id=21

22. alan kug-sig₁₇ alan {na₄}za-gin₃-na-ŋu₁₀
#lem: alan[image]; kugsig[gold]; alan[image]; zagin[lapis lazuli]
#etcsl: line-id=22

23. kisal mah e₂-niŋ₂-ŋa₂-ra-ka-na si ba-ni-sa₂-sa₂
#lem: kisal[courtyard]; mah[great]; Eniŋara[1]TN; si[horn]; sa[equal]
#etcsl: line-id=23

24. aratta kug-gin₇ gi₁₆-sa mi-ni-ŋar-ŋar
#lem: Aratta[1]GN; kug[pure]; gilsa[treasure]; ŋar[put]
#etcsl: line-id=24

25. e₂-muhaldim gal-la-ni gud udu ba-ni-ŋar
#lem: emuhaldim[kitchen]; gal[big]; gud[bull]; udu[sheep]; ŋar[put]
#etcsl: line-id=25

26. e₂-gir₄ mah-a-ni he₂-ŋal₂-la bi₂-de₆
#lem: egir[bakery]; mah[great]; heŋal[plenty]; de[carry]
#etcsl: line-id=26

27. e₂-lunga₃ zabar-re he₂-du₇-na
#lem: elungak[brewery]; zabar[bronze]; hedu[ornament]
#etcsl: line-id=27

28. kaš!(GUD)-kaš!(GUD)-bi-ta NE ki ba-ni-us₂-us₂
#lem: kaš[beer]; X; ki[place]; us[accompany]
#etcsl: line-id=28

29. kaš gig₂ kurun kaš su₄ <e₂> a₂ sikil-ba sur-ra
#lem: kaš[beer]; giggig[black]; kurun[beer]; kaš[beer]; su[red]; e[house]; a[arm]; sikil[pure]; sur[press]
#etcsl: line-id=29

30. kiŋ₂-sig unu₂ gal-la-ni ba-ni-ŋar
#lem: kiŋsig[afternoon meal]; unu[dwelling]; gal[big]; ŋar[put]
#etcsl: line-id=30

31. [...] X X [...]
#lem: X; X; X; X
#etcsl: line-id=31

